param.string: CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_company = '0073' THEN 'Open Bank S.A' ELSE 'Open Bank S.A' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_acc_currency  IN ('EUR', 'USD', 'CAD', 'NZD', 'AUD', 'JPY', 'GBP', 'CHF', 'SKR', 'DKR', 'NKR', 'DKK','NOK','SEK') THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_collateral_code IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END

CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '21305%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '2231130%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '223213%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '2232130%' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '13%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '15%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '175%' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_quotation_ind IS NULL OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_quotation_ind = '$' THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '100%' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END
CASE WHEN $Aggregation.ias_classification IN ('AFS', 'HFT') THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END
